lead_paragraph: As paths to the NBA from Europe go, Thanasis Antetokounmpo has taken the long way, but having signed a second short-term contract with  the New York Knicks and made his NBA debut, he is determined to make his stay as long as possible.

headline.print_headline: From Greece to New York, Antetokounmpo Lands With Knicks
